# Web UI

- **Stack:** HTML + CSS + JS, no build step.
- **Modules:** `api.js` (cached fetch), `species.js` (lazy species), `render-*.js`, `beaches.js` page controller, `page.js` (nav bootstrap), `verify.js` (?verify=1).
- **CSS:** Single `web/css/ocean.css` — tokens, layout, components, page sections.
- **Lazy load:** `fetch()` one JSON file per user action — see `web/README.md`.
- **No npm, no build, no test libraries** in this project.
- **No frameworks** unless user requests React/etc.
- **Pages:** Home, beaches (Curiosity), connection, conservation — shared nav via `js/nav.js`.
